hopobject.body: Have you seen any good films recently? cauli rice mediterranean The temporary fix calls for installing steel plates - shims - in gaps between bearings to prevent them from swiveling. That would effectively limit horizontal bridge movement in a major earthquake and allow the span to open well before December. Crews would continue to install a permanent fix using steel saddles and cables to strap the shear keys to the bridge piers. The shims would be removed once that work is completed.
